data.description: Room to Roam! Here is your opportunity to live on 5 acres with no deed restrictions. Spacious country home on 2 acres with another 3 wooded. This Home features spacious open living areas, a large primary bedroom and spacious primary bath with soaking tub and separate oversized shower. You enjoy watching the sunset on the spacious covered front porch. In addition, there is an oversized carport with a workshop. Don't miss the chance to own your 5-acre piece of Texas. This home will go quickly!  Schedule your showing today!
